HEADWORD: Oncidium
<hw>On*cid"i*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of tropical orchidaceous plants, the
flower of one species of which (<spn>Oncidium Papilio</spn>) resembles a
butterfly.</def>⟦br⟧
